      • calculateTotal

        public void calculateTotal()
        calculateTotal(): Populates the fields double total and String profitOrLoss. It also populates double totalUnsigned, by multiplying the total by -1 if there are losses. This is because no negative numbers should be printed in the report.

      • calculateInStock

      • getTotalUnsigned
